     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <head>Aliud in Nobilissima ejus verba suavissi<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>mae consolationis plenissima.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>QVale melos cantat sinuoso flumine Cygnus,</l>
      <l>Instantis praeco funeris ipse sui;</l>
      <l>Tale canis nuper, dum coeli gaudia cernis;</l>
      <l>Pendet ab ore pio lecta corona tuo.</l>
      <l>
         <pb facs="62"/>
Dum{que} Deo raptus contendis in aethera nisu,</l>
      <l>Mox novus ex ipso sunere factus olor.</l>
      <l>Laetus ut aeterno moduleris carmina plectro,</l>
      <l>Quéis summi resonant fulgida tecta patris:</l>
      <l>Vt{que} leves temnens curas, &amp; vota gementûm</l>
      <l>In cassum, vero jam potiare bono.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <dateline>Anno <date>1632. pridie Cal. Decembris.</date>
      </dateline>
   </closer>
</div>
